Adult mark:<i> In the 80's,</i>
<i> people were thinking of</i>

00:09.510 --> 00:11.376
<i>The dire situation in ethiopia.</i>

00:11.379 --> 00:12.911
Mary: Well, we might
starve, too.

00:12.980 --> 00:14.913
The friggin' fridge
is on the fritz again.

00:14.915 --> 00:16.315
Adult mark:<i> And then,</i>
<i> unfortunately,</i>

00:16.317 --> 00:18.317
<i> Went right back</i>
<i> to thinking of themselves.</i>

00:18.452 --> 00:20.085
There's nothing wrong
with that fridge.

00:20.087 --> 00:23.321
That fridge is gonna
outlive us all.

